  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Imagine inheriting a farm AND a shop.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What would you do with it? Yes, it's a mess. Yes, it needs work. But it's yours—and without a mortgage. In this economy?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/db1d6689d156eb6b76a795edc9e1669b.poster.avif?t=1737572444\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/db1d6689d156eb6b76a795edc9e1669b.webm?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/db1d6689d156eb6b76a795edc9e1669b.mp4?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Restore Your Farm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform this abandoned land into the thriving farm it deserves to be. <br>Grow your own crops, take care of animals (coming soon), and upgrade your surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It'll take effort, but soon you'll be able to acquire new tools, improve your buildings, and customize the farm of your dreams.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/e808963dd21dd8dbfdf7400afccde4a2.poster.avif?t=1737572444\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/e808963dd21dd8dbfdf7400afccde4a2.webm?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/e808963dd21dd8dbfdf7400afccde4a2.mp4?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Your Dream Store</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why sell your crops and produce to someone else when you can do it yourself?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever heard of a farmer's market? Well, this shop has the \"farmer\" part sorted. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organize your shop, manage the goods on your shelves, and handle all the finances!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to leave your customers satisfied - they can and they will write a review.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/c7cc613327ae8f8b11209628314c7835.poster.avif?t=1737572444\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/c7cc613327ae8f8b11209628314c7835.webm?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/c7cc613327ae8f8b11209628314c7835.mp4?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hire Someone To Do The Job</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feeling lazy? We all have been here - just hire help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tending the shop and carrying heavy boxes can be tiring. It's only natural to want someone to do it for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Luckily, there are always people who like money and are willing to work for it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just don't forget to pay salaries. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/24d8ca9d37517fa4f6e35348e1219a22.poster.avif?t=1737572444\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/24d8ca9d37517fa4f6e35348e1219a22.webm?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/24d8ca9d37517fa4f6e35348e1219a22.mp4?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Master the Art of Multitasking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Running a farm and a shop at the same time isn’t easy. But you’ve got this!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balance your time between tending to crops, serving customers, and managing the chaos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you focus on strict business? Go personal and sustainable? Maybe a bit of both? Only you can decide.<br><br><strong>This game is in early access so some features may still be in development.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the moment, the game is fully translated into English, with machine translations for other languages. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Here are some of the plans for the future:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farm animals</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bees.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Greenhouse.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More customization.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farm and storage expansions.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More diversity in produce and customers.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have ideas, or suggestions or want to offer help with translation in your language - feel free to contact us in Discord.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Imagine inheriting a farm AND a shop.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What would you do with it? Yes, it's a mess. Yes, it needs work. But it's yours—and without a mortgage. In this economy?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/db1d6689d156eb6b76a795edc9e1669b.poster.avif?t=1737572444\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/db1d6689d156eb6b76a795edc9e1669b.webm?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/db1d6689d156eb6b76a795edc9e1669b.mp4?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Restore Your Farm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform this abandoned land into the thriving farm it deserves to be. <br>Grow your own crops, take care of animals (coming soon), and upgrade your surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It'll take effort, but soon you'll be able to acquire new tools, improve your buildings, and customize the farm of your dreams.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/e808963dd21dd8dbfdf7400afccde4a2.poster.avif?t=1737572444\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/e808963dd21dd8dbfdf7400afccde4a2.webm?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/e808963dd21dd8dbfdf7400afccde4a2.mp4?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Your Dream Store</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why sell your crops and produce to someone else when you can do it yourself?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever heard of a farmer's market? Well, this shop has the \"farmer\" part sorted. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organize your shop, manage the goods on your shelves, and handle all the finances!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to leave your customers satisfied - they can and they will write a review.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/c7cc613327ae8f8b11209628314c7835.poster.avif?t=1737572444\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/c7cc613327ae8f8b11209628314c7835.webm?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/c7cc613327ae8f8b11209628314c7835.mp4?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hire Someone To Do The Job</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feeling lazy? We all have been here - just hire help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tending the shop and carrying heavy boxes can be tiring. It's only natural to want someone to do it for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Luckily, there are always people who like money and are willing to work for it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just don't forget to pay salaries. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/24d8ca9d37517fa4f6e35348e1219a22.poster.avif?t=1737572444\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/24d8ca9d37517fa4f6e35348e1219a22.webm?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975460/extras/24d8ca9d37517fa4f6e35348e1219a22.mp4?t=1737572444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Master the Art of Multitasking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Running a farm and a shop at the same time isn’t easy. But you’ve got this!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Balance your time between tending to crops, serving customers, and managing the chaos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you focus on strict business? Go personal and sustainable? Maybe a bit of both? Only you can decide.<br><br><strong>This game is in early access so some features may still be in development.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the moment, the game is fully translated into English, with machine translations for other languages. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Here are some of the plans for the future:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farm animals</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bees.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Greenhouse.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More customization.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farm and storage expansions.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More diversity in produce and customers.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have ideas, or suggestions or want to offer help with translation in your language - feel free to contact us in Discord.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
